{"article_id":"XxKXIBYZC94ZXmn9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Congress returns Monday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"staring at another deadline","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to finance the Department of Homeland Security .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"instead of stalling again ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"lawmakers look more likely this time to steer the anti-terrorism agency away from the funding cliff through September .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"With the clock ticking until the new Friday deadline","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"to avert a DHS funding lapse ,","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"the GOP-controlled Senate will take the first step with a vote Monday","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"on whether to head into formal negotiations with the House","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"on financing the security agency .","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"Senate Democrats are expected to block that move .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"That will put the onus squarely back on Speaker John Boehner and his leadership team .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Democrats fully expect the speaker to allow a vote on a so-called clean DHS funding measure","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that runs until the end of the fiscal year .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"But Republicans were coy over the weekend about what they ' ll do ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"promising only","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"that they ' ll continue battling President Barack Obama ' s executive actions on immigration .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"\" We want to get a conference with the Senate , \"","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Boehner said Sunday on CBS ' \" Face the Nation. \"","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"\" Now ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"[ Senate Democrats have ] made clear","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"that they don ' t want to go to conference .","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"But they ' re going to have a vote .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"If they vote , in fact , not to get a conference ,","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"this bill may be coming back to the House . \"","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"The messy maneuvering wasn ' t what Republican leaders had in mind","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"when they took the reins of both chambers in January .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Much of their early tenure has been marked by infighting over their response to Obama ' s unilateral immigration moves .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Republicans have tried to find a way","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"to fund DHS","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"and at the same time foil the president on immigration ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"but they ' ve been blocked by Democrats at every turn .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Last week , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"split off DHS financing from measures","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to stymie the immigration actions ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and the Senate passed a clean funding bill with a 68-31 vote on Friday .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"But the more raucous and unpredictable House wasn ' t ready to capitulate ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"openly defying the GOP leadership on the House floor","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"by defeating its plan","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"to fund DHS for three weeks .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"A scramble ensued .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Late Friday night ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"just hours before DHS was set to run out of money ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Capitol Hill coalesced around a seven-day DHS funding fix .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Obama signed it into law minutes before midnight .","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"The weeklong extension came","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"after Democratic aides reported","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"reaching a deal with Republicans :","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"House Democrats would provide the votes","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to get it approved ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and , in return , Boehner would allow a vote this week","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"to fund DHS through September .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Democrats said","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"it was predicated on the Senate rejecting Republicans ' request","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to negotiate a compromise funding deal .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"\" Your vote tonight will assure","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that we will vote for full funding next week , \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Pelosi wrote in a \" Dear Colleague \" letter to House Democrats on Friday night .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"\" There is no such deal .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"There is no such bill , \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"House Majority Whip Steve Scalise","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"( R-La . )","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"said on \" Fox News Sunday . \"","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Boehner said Sunday","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"the only agreement with Pelosi was to follow \" regular order . \"","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"But Democrats would not have backed a seven-day DHS funding patch","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"without some assurance from Boehner","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that he would put a DHS bill free of immigration provisions","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"attacking Obama ' s executive actions on the House floor .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"\" There was no ambiguity whatsoever , \"","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"a top congressional aide said Sunday ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that Boehner , McConnell , Pelosi and Senate Minority Leader Harry Reid","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"( D-Nev. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"as well as Obama , were all clear on the terms of the deal .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Boehner will also have to watch the reaction from the hard-line conservatives","depth":4},{"id":78,"text":"who were behind Friday ' s embarrassing defeat .","depth":4},{"id":79,"text":"The speaker ' s allies have fretted","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"that conservative opponents of Boehner may mount a coup","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"to overthrow the Ohio Republican .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"But one leader of the activist wing of the House GOP said Sunday","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"that no oust-Boehner plan is in the works .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"\" That ' s not gon na happen , \"","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"said Rep. Jim Jordan","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"( R-Ohio ) ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"who leads the newly created House Freedom Caucus ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"on CNN .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Still , other Republicans want Boehner and his team to find a way","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"to move beyond the conference ' s hard-right faction","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"that has repeatedly bucked the leaders .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"\" There ' s an element within our party ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"there ' s a wing within the Congress","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"which is absolutely irresponsible , \"","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Rep. Peter King","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"( R-N.Y. )","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"said Sunday on ABC .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"\" They have no concept of reality .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Listen ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"I am as opposed to this immigration action","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"as they are .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"But the fact is ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"it ' s essential that we fund the Department of Homeland Security . \"","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"King added","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"that \" there ' s no doubt","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"[ a clean DHS measure ] would pass , \"","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"although House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"( R-Calif. )","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"said on NBC","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that \" as of now , \" a funding bill","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"without the immigration provisions","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"would not clear the House .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Doing so would require the support of about 30 House Republicans","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"if all Democrats support the clean bill ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"as expected .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Though the drama","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"that unfolded Friday on the House floor","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"was undoubtedly a defeat to Boehner and the rest of his leadership team ,","depth":4},{"id":119,"text":"the speaker downplayed the rifts as a dispute over strategy rather than the GOP ' s ultimate goal","depth":4},{"id":120,"text":"of stopping Obama ' s actions .","depth":4},{"id":121,"text":"\" It was just messy ,","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"and I ' m not into messy , \"","depth":5},{"id":123,"text":"Boehner said on CBS of Friday ' s chaos .","depth":4},{"id":124,"text":"\" But listen ,","depth":4},{"id":125,"text":"I enjoy being in a legislative body .","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"I enjoy all the personalities .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"And I ' ve got a lot of them . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":255,"left":243,"right":254,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":204,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":170,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":156,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":133,"right":155,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":130,"right":132,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":0,"right":129,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":3,"right":131,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":131,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":152,"right":15